author: USA TODAY, Adrienne Dunn, USA TODAY
title: Fact check: Claim of new symptoms for COVID-19 is partly false
description: Neither the CDC nor WHO lists vomiting or loss of appetite as symptoms of the virus, and diarrhea is very rarely reported.
content:
